# ==============================================================================
# JobApplicationAgent Authentication Configuration
# ==============================================================================
# Select one of the two modes below to configure local authentication.
# By default, the application will attempt to use Vertex AI if GOOGLE_GENAI_USE_VERTEXAI
# is set to True (or not specified).

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# OPTION 1: Google AI Studio (Recommended for rapid development)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 1. Obtain an API key from Google AI Studio: https://aistudio.google.com/
# 2. Uncomment and populate the variables below:

# GOOGLE_GENAI_USE_VERTEXAI=False
# GEMINI_API_KEY=your_google_ai_studio_api_key_here

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# OPTION 2: Google Cloud / Vertex AI (Enterprise / Production)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 1. Install the Google Cloud CLI (gcloud) and run:
#    gcloud auth application-default login
# 2. Uncomment and populate the variables below:

# GOOGLE_GENAI_USE_VERTEXAI=True
# GOOGLE_CLOUD_PROJECT=your_gcp_project_id_here
# GOOGLE_CLOUD_LOCATION=us-east1
